summary: This code imports necessary classes from different modules within the q_transformer package, including QRoboticTransformer, MaxViT, QLearner, Agent, ReplayMemoryDataset, and BaseEnvironment. These classes are used for building the transformer-based agent architecture and learning algorithms for reinforcement learning tasks.
